>> PROGDIR:, I though I updated my Frank Willie's PPC emul library ?
>This didn't work for me either.

Things that cause awinquakeppc v0.2 (29/12/1999) to crash:

(1) Not having at least KS3.1
(2) Not having cybergraphics.library  (either CGX or P96)
(3) Not setting the stack to at least about 500000 first

If you get the message "file is not executable", try using runelf.  If
it still won't load, you probably need a newer ppc.library (or newer
ppc.library emulation).

I fixed (2) for v0.3 which I uploaded to Aminet 3 days ago.  However
it still wasn't it game/shoot last time I looked.  Frank Wille and
Steffen Haeuser's version is faster and has more features anyway...

Regards,
